title: Tests: Former Hawkeye Sash died from mix of methadone, hydrocodone
text:
Published By: Iowa City Press - Today 
Toxicology results reveal that the former Iowa Hawkeye died from an accidental "mixed drug toxicity involving methadone and hydrocodone."
